# 3. あの子との出会い

Little Ichika: Okay, these are... Lady's tresses. It's cute how they have so many little flowers coiled around them.
Ichika's Father: Yes, that's a nice find. You're up to ten now, aren't you?
Little Ichika: Yup! I'm almost done making my flower encyclopedia for school!
Little Ichika: Thanks for helping me, Dad. My plan was to make this with Saki and the others, but we couldn't find a good time to meet.
Ichika's Father: I had fun during our walk as well. Thank you for inviting me, Ichika.
Little Ichika: Hehe. I'm really glad...! I'm gonna show Mom once it's finished.
Ichika's Father: Yes, she's going to be so proud.
Ichika's Father: Oh, they're selling gelato over there... It's starting to get a little warm, so why don't we go buy some?
Little Ichika: Oh...! I want vanilla!
Little Ichika: But I'm still not finished with my encyclopedia...
Ichika's Father: Haha. Then, I'll go buy some while you keep working on that.
Ichika's Father: Here, I'll even leave the tablet with you so that you can look up any other new flowers you find.
Little Ichika: Really...? Thanks, Dad!
Little Ichika: Let's see... What other flowers are there...?
Little Ichika: Oh, those pink ones! I'll use them.
Little Ichika: What are these? I'll try looking them up on the tablet...
Little Ichika: Oh...!
Miku: <Thanks for coming today, everyone! I hope you're looking forward to hearing me sing a lot!>
Little Ichika: What do I do...?
Little Ichika: (I tapped something and made Dad's tablet play this video...)
Little Ichika: (Who's this green-haired girl?)
Little Ichika: (Oh, she started singing... I've never heard this song before...)
Miku: ♪————————!
Little Ichika: ...!
Little Ichika: Wow! She's so amazing...!
Little Ichika: Her voice is beautiful... And it's so cool how she can play the guitar...!
Little Ichika: What's her name?
Little Ichika: Hatsune Miku?
Little Ichika: Her name's Miku...?
Ichika's Father: Ichika, I got some of that gelato for us. Let's have this while we take a break.
Little Ichika: Oh, okay...!
Little Ichika: Dad, look! This Hatsune Miku person's video popped up, and she's really cool!
Little Ichika: The song from this video's also really cool...
Little Ichika: (That other song was also pretty cool, but this one feels more like one that an idol would sing. It's really cute...)
Little Ichika: (It's so interesting how the same Miku can sing all these different types of songs...)
Little Ichika: (That also goes for each video. And depending on what she's singing, she'll sound cute, cool, grown-up and stuff... It's like she's someone new every time.)
Little Ichika: (But it's the same Hatsune Miku in all of them...)
Little Ichika: That's so amazing...
Little Ichika: But...
Miku: ♪————————!
Little Ichika: I still think this song's the coolest...
Little Ichika: She shines so bright, and she sounds like she's having so much fun...
Little Ichika: I...
Little Ichika: (I want to do that...!)
Little Ichika: (I want to be just like her!)
Little Honami: Wait, play it...?
Little Ichika: Yeah!
Little Ichika: We should play a Miku song together!
Little Shiho: Miku...? As in Hatsune Miku? The VIRTUAL SINGER?
Little Saki: Have you always liked Miku, Ichi?
Little Ichika: I just found out about her yesterday! Here, this song... You need to hear it!
Little Shiho: Oh, this is a pretty cool song...
Little Ichika: See what I mean?
Little Saki: Miku's also really cool!
Little Ichika: I know, right?!
Little Honami: But how are we supposed to play this?
Little Shiho: Does that mean we're forming a band? I can play the bass.
Little Saki: Oh, my mom taught me how to play the piano! I can play that!
Little Shiho: Not many bands have pianos. What if you played the keyboard?
Little Saki: Like an electronic one? I can play one of those♪
Little Ichika: My dad owns a guitar, so I'll ask to see if I can borrow it!
Little Saki: Wow, Ichi, that's so cool!
Little Ichika: I-It's not like he's said yes yet...
Little Shiho: But I'm sure he will. I mean, your dad's such a nice person.
Little Saki: Exactly! That just leaves...
Little Honami: What other instruments do bands have...?
Little Shiho: Normally, a set of drums...
Little Honami: Drums... Like the ones in the music room?
Little Honami: But I've never played the drums before...
Little Ichika: We'll also need a vocalist...
Little Honami: What?! A-As in singing? No, I can't do that...!
Little Saki: Oh, what about the triangle or recorder?!
Little Honami: Th-Those might work for me...
Little Shiho: But we're talking about a band here.
Little Saki: So, drums?
Little Honami: Oh...
Little Ichika: I'm sorry, Honami... I didn't mean to make you panic or anything.
Little Ichika: But would you be willing to give it a try...?
Little Ichika: You can always pick a different instrument if you think they're too hard to play after you try practicing with them.
Little Ichika: I've never played the guitar before either, so I have no idea how that's going to go...
Little Ichika: But I want to play with you, Honami. I want us to all play together...!
Little Honami: Ichika...
Little Honami: O-Okay...
Little Honami: I'll give it a try.
Little Ichika: ...! Thank you, Honami!
Little Ichika: Let's get our band started!
